---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About CloudPriceFinder.com" description="Learn more about CloudPriceFinder.com - the open-source multi-cloud cost comparison tool">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        About CloudPriceFinder.com
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Open-source multi-cloud instance cost comparison
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
      <h2>What is CloudPriceFinder.com?</h2>
      <p>
        CloudPriceFinder.com is an open-source tool that helps developers and businesses compare 
        cloud instance costs across multiple providers. Instead of manually checking 
        each cloud provider's pricing pages, CloudPriceFinder.com aggregates and normalizes 
        pricing data to help you make informed decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Supported Providers</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hetzner Cloud</strong> - Fully integrated with real-time API data</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Web Services (AWS)</strong> - Coming soon</li>
        <li><strong>Microsoft Azure</strong> - Coming soon</li>
        <li><strong>Google Cloud Platform (GCP)</strong> - Coming soon</li>
        <li><strong>Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI)</strong> - Coming soon</li>
        <li><strong>OVH</strong> - Coming soon</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Real-time pricing data from provider APIs</li>
        <li>Standardized comparison across providers</li>
        <li>Filter by CPU, memory, price, and region</li>
        <li>Sort by any specification</li>
        <li>Mobile-responsive design</li>
        <li>No tracking or analytics</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Sources</h2>
      <p>
        CloudPriceFinder.com fetches data directly from cloud provider APIs when available, 
        ensuring the most accurate and up-to-date pricing information. All prices 
        are converted to USD for easy comparison while preserving original pricing 
        in the provider's currency.
      </p>

      <h2>Open Source</h2>
      <p>
        CloudPriceFinder.com is completely open source and available on GitHub.
      </p>
      
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Contributing</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-800 mb-4">
          Help us add more cloud providers or improve the existing functionality.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="https://github.com/eSKylezZ/CloudPriceFinder/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
        >
          View on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>